name: UPrimaryAssetLabel
doc: A seed file that is created to mark referenced assets as part of this primary asset

Rules: Management rules for this specific asset, if set it will override the type rules
ExplicitAssets: List of manually specified assets to label
ExplicitBlueprints: List of manually specified blueprint assets to label
AssetCollection: Collection to load asset references out of
bLabelAssetsInMyDirectory: True to Label everything in this directory and sub directories
bIsRuntimeLabel: Set to true if the label asset itself should be cooked and available at runtime. This does not affect the assets that are labeled, they are set with cook rule
bIncludeRedirectors: If true, redirectors found by the AssetLabel's explicit assets or directory will be labeled. If false, redirectors will be skipped.
